      interface  IdInt
      A list of integers nested in list of ids.Ids are there to avoid OptimisticLockFailures from different writers.Typical use of the int list is to generate data change notifications.Config is true, in order to allow Restconf reset content at will.Expected writes should create and delete items at random, values 0 .. 2^20.
